islike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:01:41.000Z","msg":"衝啊"},{"pid":"9afdf8a50e053df8b2425f77e33191fd78f62c26","tid":1606521,"uid":205469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:02:24.000Z","msg":"charge!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c8b51b11f2ba56ae0afb00f1bbd425f1e406b6b","tid":1606521,"uid":108502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:02:46.000Z","msg":"衝"},{"pid":"2648957b0652edf369f69f478770936b40e71f15","tid":1606521,"uid":60049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:03:44.000Z","msg":"衝"},{"pid":"11ae86c1c907e1a54431bffd9f7415ef5b9db4a8","tid":1606521,"uid":297230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:03:51.000Z","msg":"Telegram 預設訊息可以保護到手足性命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kCXiwqP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCXiwqP.png&h=5c04cb99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n星火 TG: @Abccbbc<br />\n612 TG: @ReliefFund612<br />\nPush"},{"pid":"fcacf9de620d92ab6c51c62e1761c2368dd29852","tid":1606521,"uid":275366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:03:53.000Z","msg":"香港人 衝啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea932171f8bda7529bf0e07ad8b6b6943a7cbdc","tid":1606521,"uid":270237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:03:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日出去前睇左先</span></span><br />\n來自CSD職員既提醒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603297</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n你班勇武手足,同我聽住,有部份前線手足認識我地,之前幾場戰役我地合作過,最初有人以為我地係鬼,詳細唔多講,我地係一班受過專業防暴訓練懲教署職員,之前已經係現場教過大家,如何組織防線同攻擊防暴,之前都有唔少進步,但今日我地冇出現,你地表現太差,中要咁多比人拉,我好心痛..<br />\n我地人手有限,身份問題,冇可能次次出現,我係度比些少資訊大家,希望大家務必share同發輝得好D<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.速龍都係人,佢地咩住咁重裝備同蒙面先至令信心大增,但大家留意下佢地人手一定唔夠手足多,只要大家穩固防線,只要佢地一跑出嚟,手足唔走向前攻,先用人火同磚頭攻,再快速向前推進, 趁機會足幾個差人抬去自己方向,呢個時候繼續用磚頭攻擊,同時向差人方向口射洗潔精地下,務別令佢地仆街,最重要立即除佢哋面具,之後私了..佢地以後就會驚..</span></span><br />\n2.佩槍唔係向上蚊,而係向內45度角向前推,大家明點做😁<br />\n3.如果執到警槍,同佢地玩過遊戲,逐粒子彈唔小心跌落坑渠,洗手間,包保玩殘佢地...<br />\n4.咁黑仔有狗用槍指你,可行情況試下用1秒用長竹,或雨傘打佢手同向上..<br />\n5如果打狗,唔該搵手足集中打腳,上半身有盾牌你打係冇用,要傷腳同關節先有足,以上除左增強攻擊同防護能力之外,就係要令到狗驚,你要記住佢地都係人,唔係超人...<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">6.哨兵必須去遠少少,手足唔好集足一個地方,必須快速移動,不停向唔同地方攻擊,切斷差人增援,攻擊完立即走人,玩殘班狗..</span></span><br />\n7.盡量引班狗去橋下,用高空方式攻擊..<br />\n最後10.1見,大家努力<br />\n一班CSD職員上<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CoSeSaV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCoSeSaV.jpg&h=a1f189f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2EqTohB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2EqTohB.jpg&h=64c3cc95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7b585710e37e70eec9d4b8e9127fa6742f7c152","tid":1606521,"uid":160107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:05:14.000Z","msg":"衝呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a8116ac1a34b4fc7a19b962490f054ebafa7ec","tid":1606521,"uid":80763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:07:37.000Z","msg":"衝"},{"pid":"4c7a8e9aa9a779176eb42c11b22e8a742cee56c8","tid":1606521,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:08:17.000Z","msg":"衝佢老母"},{"pid":"9a7461a02e1d693ccdb3c23deb510e18d9d62317","tid":1606521,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:09:37.000Z","msg":"衝啊"},{"pid":"811da799409dbd740aef301db435a98e791d99de","tid":1606521,"uid":302,"like":0,